relatedBlades.title: Secure Your Spot at Cloudflare's Exclusive Pickleball Event!
relatedBlades.copy:
Cloudflare is thrilled to invite you to an exclusive pickleball event. Brush up your serve and enhance your cybersecurity knowledge with experts from the field! This unique occasion offers an exceptional opportunity to network with peers, participate in an exciting game of pickleball, and learn how to safeguard your digital assets more effectively.

Here's what you can look forward to:

- __In-depth insights__ on preempting advanced cyber-attacks with our multi-layered security solutions.
- __Expert-led lightning talk__ on Adaptive DDoS Protection, Bot management, Zero Trust Security, Email Security, and Remote Browser Isolation.
- __Unforgettable experiences__ as you engage in a friendly pickleball match, fostering connections and learn from professional players.
- __Networking opportunities__ with like-minded individuals in the cybersecurity arena.

Remember, seats for this event are limited. So don't wait â€” RSVP now to secure your place!

*Join us, and together let's make cybersecurity a lot more fun!*

__Event Details:__</br>
Date: Thursday, August 24, 2023</br> 
Time: 3:00PM - 6:00PM PT</br> 
Location: Bay Club Broadway Tennis & Pickleball, 60 Edwards Court, Burlingame, CA 94010</br> 

__Agenda:__ </br>
3:00 - 3:30 Welcome and Expert-led lightening talk</br>
3:30 - 4:00 Intro to pickleball clinic</br>
4:00 - 5:00 Pickleball shuffle play</br>
5:00 - 6:00 Networking with food and drinks</br> 

<sub>Please note, we have space for a limited number of players. Your spot is not confirmed until you receive official confirmation.</sub>
